<?php
return ['messages'=>['#https://eji.com.hk/portfolio_group/jewellery-exhibitions/'=>'#https://eji.com.hk/portfolio_group/jewellery-exhibitions/','<h4><a href="https://eji.com.hk/the-mastery-behind-our-craft-excellence-in-every-facet-of-our-jewellery-manufacturing/">The Mastery Behind Our Craft: Excellence in Every Facet of Our Jewellery Manufacturing</a></h4>'=>'<h4><a href="https://eji.com.hk/zh-hans/%e5%b7%a5%e8%89%ba%e8%83%8c%e5%90%8e%e7%9a%84%e7%b2%be%e6%b9%9b%e6%8a%80%e8%89%ba%ef%bc%9a%e7%8f%a0%e5%ae%9d%e5%88%b6%e9%80%a0%e7%9a%84%e6%af%8f%e4%b8%80%e4%b8%aa%e7%8e%af%e8%8a%82%e9%83%bd%e7%b2%be/">工艺背后的精湛技艺：精益求精的珠宝制造</a></h4>','<h5>June 20, Thursday - June 22, Saturday<br />10am - 6pm</h5><h5>June 23, Sunday<br />10am - 5pm</h5>'=>'<h5>6 月 20 日星期四至 6 月 22 日星期六<br>上午 10 时至下午 6 时</h5><h5>6月23日，星期日<br>上午10点至下午5点</h5>','<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: Poppins;">Hong Kong, an ever-bustling metropolis, is not just a global business hub; but also a vibrant canvas for cultural and artistic utterances. Have you ever had a chance to explore different places in this city, apart from attending international jewellery fairs and engaging in business appointments? If you are planning a visit to Hong Kong for the <a href="https://eji.com.hk/portfolio/jewellery-gem-fair-asia-2024/">Jewellery and Gem Asia Fair</a> this June, enrich your stay with these spectacular cultural experiences that promise to mesmerize and inspire. From traditional events to modern art, there’s something for every taste.</span></p>'=>'<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: Poppins;">香港是一个充满活力的大都市，不仅是全球商业中心，也是文化和艺术的活跃舞台。除了参加国际珠宝展和商务洽谈，您是否有机会探索这座城市的不同角落？如果您计划在今年 6 月来香港参加<a href="https://eji.com.hk/portfolio/jewellery-gem-fair-asia-2024/">亚洲珠宝首饰展览会</a>，那么这些精彩纷呈的文化体验一定会让您流连忘返。从传统活动到现代艺术，总有一款适合您的口味。   </span></p>','<p>Before your hectic schedule for the Jewellery and Gem Asia Fair, kick off your journey with a bang on the stunning marine pyrotechnic displays at Victoria Harbour on June 15, 2024. These will light up the night sky alongside the multimedia show, “A Symphony of Lights”, which features spectacular lights and music. The breathtaking views of the skyline and Victoria Harbour are sure to impress. More details can be found on the <a href="https://www.discoverhongkong.com/eng/what-s-new/harbour-nightscape-spectacle.html">Hong Kong Tourism Board website</a>.</p>'=>'<p>在您参加亚洲珠宝首饰展览会的繁忙日程之前，2024 年 6 月 15 日在维多利亚港举行的令人惊叹的海洋烟火表演将为您的旅程拉开序幕。这些烟火将与多媒体表演 "幻彩咏香江"（A Symphony of Lights）一起点亮夜空，其中包括壮观的灯光和音乐。届时，天际线和维多利亚港的壮丽景色定会给人留下深刻印象。更多详情可浏览<a href="https://www.discoverhongkong.com/eng/what-s-new/harbour-nightscape-spectacle.html">香港旅游发展局网站</a>。   </p>','<p>Delve into the multisensory world of floral art blossom at the renowned Naked Flowers Hong Kong Art Exhibition by Japanese artist Ryotaro Muramatsu. This immersive experience offers a unique perspective and inspiration on nature’s aesthetics. Tickets are available for $180 at <a href="https://hk.trip.com/travel-guide/attraction/hong-kong/uob-kayhian-presents-naked-flowers-hong-kong-145018737/?locale=en_hk">Trip.com</a>. Don’t miss this captivating art adventure if you appreciate art and nature.</p>'=>'<p>在日本艺术家 Ryotaro Muramatsu（村松龙太郎）著名的《裸花香港艺术展》（Naked Flowers Hong Kong Art Exhibition）上，深入花卉艺术绽放的多感官世界。这种身临其境的体验将为您提供一个独特的视角，激发您对自然美学的灵感。门票在<a href="https://hk.trip.com/travel-guide/attraction/hong-kong/uob-kayhian-presents-naked-flowers-hong-kong-145018737/?locale=en_hk">Trip.com</a> 上的售价为 180 美元。如果您欣赏艺术和自然，千万不要错过这次迷人的艺术之旅。   </p>','<p>Experience the charm of old Hong Kong at Lin Heung Lau, a 135-year-old tea house that has recently reopened at its original site on Wellington Street. Known for serving traditional dim sum in an old-fashioned way – with rushed staff pushing trolley carts loaded with bamboo steamers - this is the perfect place to savor the city’s culinary heritage and indulge in a bit of nostalgia. Discover more about this iconic location <a href="https://www.afoodieworld.com/blog/2024/04/03/lin-heung-lau-teahouse-reopens/">here</a>.</p>'=>'<p>最近，这家拥有 135 年历史的茶餐厅在威灵顿街的原址重新开业，让您体验老香港的魅力。这家茶餐厅以提供传统点心而闻名，店员推着装满竹制蒸笼的手推车，步履匆匆。<a href="https://www.afoodieworld.com/blog/2024/04/03/lin-heung-lau-teahouse-reopens/">点击此处</a>，了解更多关于这个标志性地点的信息。  </p>','<p>Explore the dynamic world of street art at the HKwalls Street Art Festival, where international and local artists transform the city’s walls to into vibrant, large murals and artworks. This festival is a splendid visual feast that showcases the creative pulse of Hong Kong. Be sure to capture these instagrammable street arts around the town and dive into the colourful vibes at <a href="https://www.hkwalls.org/festivals/hkwalls-2024/">HKwalls 2024</a>!</p>'=>'<p>在香港墙街艺术节（HKwalls Street Art Festival）上探索充满活力的街头艺术世界。在这里，国际和本地艺术家将城市的墙壁改造成充满活力的大型壁画和艺术作品。这个艺术节是一场精彩绝伦的视觉盛宴，展现了香港的创意脉搏。请务必在城中捕捉这些可以用 instagram 记录的街头艺术，并沉浸在<a href="https://www.hkwalls.org/festivals/hkwalls-2024/">2024 年香港墙</a>艺术节的多彩氛围中！  </p>','<p>Immerse yourself in the competitive spirit and cultural pageantry of the Hong Kong International Dragon Boat Races on June 15 &amp; 16, 2024. Witness thousands of dragon boat athletes from around the world paddling fiercely along the Tsim Sha Tsui East harbourfront. This exhilarating event is a must-see for its vibrant atmosphere and thrilling races in the birthplace of modern dragon boat racing. Learn more about the event <a href="https://www.discoverhongkong.com/eng/what-s-new/events/dhk-highlighted-events/dragon-boat-races.html">here</a>.</p>'=>'<p>2024 年 6 月 15 日和 16 日，您将沉浸在香港国际龙舟赛的竞技精神和文化盛况之中。来自世界各地的数千名龙舟运动员将在尖东海滨激烈划桨。在现代龙舟赛的发源地，这项令人兴奋的赛事气氛热烈，比赛惊险刺激，是不容错过的盛事。<a href="https://www.discoverhongkong.com/eng/what-s-new/events/dhk-highlighted-events/dragon-boat-races.html">点击此处</a>了解更多赛事信息。   </p>','<p>Whether you are an art and cultural enthusiast, spend some time walking through the city. These experiences in Hong Kong will undoubtedly add a memorable richness to your business trip to <a href="https://eji.com.hk/portfolio/jewellery-gem-fair-asia-2024/">Jewellery and Gem Asia Fair</a>. Don’t forget to visit us to explore our fabulous new collections and experience our exceptional bespoke services. It is also a perfect opportunity to share your discoveries and insights from your visits.</p><p>We are confident that the hidden gems of Hong Kong will enrich your experiences in the city like never before. This time, the unique charm and vibrant culture of Hong Kong will surely make you fall in love with this fascinating place!</p>'=>'<p>无论您是艺术和文化爱好者，还是花些时间漫步这座城市。这些在香港的体验无疑会为您的<a href="https://eji.com.hk/portfolio/jewellery-gem-fair-asia-2024/">亚洲珠宝首饰展览会</a>商务之旅增添难忘的色彩。不要忘了参观我们的新产品系列，体验我们卓越的定制服务。这也是分享您的参观发现和见解的绝佳机会。   </p><p>我们相信，香港隐藏的瑰宝将为您带来前所未有的丰富体验。这一次，香港的独特魅力和充满活力的文化一定会让您爱上这个迷人的地方！ </p>','Contact Our Sales Experts'=>'联系我们的销售专家','HKwalls Street Art Festival'=>'香港墙街艺术节','Historic Yumcha at Lin Heung Lau'=>'历史悠久的临香楼煎茶馆','Hong Kong International Dragon Boat Races'=>'香港国际龙舟赛','More Jewellery Exhibitions'=>'更多珠宝展','Naked Flowers Hong Kong Art Exhibition'=>'裸花香港艺术展','Opening Hour'=>'开放时间','Photograph: Facebook @Lin Heung Tea House '=>'照片Facebook @临香茶楼  ','Photograph: HKwalls'=>'摄影：香港墙','Photograph: Hong Kong China Dragon Boat Association'=>'摄影：香港中华龙舟协会','Photograph: Hong Kong Tourism Board'=>'照片：香港旅游发展局香港旅游发展局','Photograph: Instagram @naked_inc'=>'照片Instagram @naked_inc','Pyrotechnic Displays'=>'烟火表演','READ MORE'=>'阅读更多','Register Now'=>'立即注册','caption-image-28ae7e5'=>'照片Instagram @naked_inc','caption-image-6f816a9'=>'摄影：香港中华龙舟协会','caption-image-997e63d'=>'照片：香港旅游发展局香港旅游发展局','caption-image-9f767e8'=>'摄影：香港墙','caption-image-a28d2da'=>'照片Facebook @临香茶楼  ','editor-text-editor-08d4874'=>'<h5>6 月 20 日星期四至 6 月 22 日星期六<br>上午 10 时至下午 6 时</h5><h5>6月23日，星期日<br>上午10点至下午5点</h5>','editor-text-editor-691aa82'=>'<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: Poppins;">香港是一个充满活力的大都市，不仅是全球商业中心，也是文化和艺术的活跃舞台。除了参加